text: Unni Holmen (born 23 September 1952) is a Norwegian artistic gymnast. She was born in Oslo. She competed at the 1968 Summer Olympics and the 1972 Summer Olympics. == References == == External links == * Category:1952 births Category:Living people Category:People from Oslo Category:Norwegian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Norway Category:Gymnasts at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1972 Summer Olympics
